    ndd(p) /Wmaize 4806000, YMaize 3721000, Wheat 138500, Soya 162000, Sorghum 3366600, Sunflower 676000, Beef_cattle 722000, Mutton_sheep 9730285.71, Pork_pig 2119622.95, broilers_chicken 875000, Layers_eggs 5594042258, Dairy_cattle 2184000000/
